      <p><a href="ch77s17.html#PsionicMonsters153">Maenads</a> typically stand more than 6 feet tall and weigh about 200 pounds; males are the same height as and only marginally heavier than <a href="ch77s17.html#PsionicMonsters153">maenad</a> females. <a href="ch77s17.html#PsionicMonsters153">Maenads</a> have no facial or body hair, and they prefer heavier clothing and armor if possible.</p>
      <p><a href="ch77s17.html#PsionicMonsters153">Maenads</a> speak their own language and Common.</p>
