          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Psi-Like Abilities:</strong></span> 1/day-<span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch57.html#PsionicPowersD-F93">energy ray</a></em></span>. A <a href="ch77s17.html#PsionicMonsters153">maenad</a> can deal only sonic damage with this ability. Manifester level equal to 1/2 Hit Dice (minimum 1st). The save DC is Charisma-based.</p>
